OL,6,FThe inquiry is probing whether the
OL,7,F1998 Real IRA massacre, which claimed
OL,8,F29 lives, including a woman pregnant
OL,9,Fwith twins, could have been prevented
OL,10,Fby UK state authorities.
OL,12,FIt was established after a High Court
OL,13,Fjudgment recommended a public inquiry
OL,14,Finto alleged security failings in the
OL,15,Flead-up to the atrocity.
OL,17,FThe Irish Government has formally
OL,18,Fagreed to provide assistance to the
OL,19,Finquiry, which held its first public
OL,20,Fhearing in July.
