OL,6,FIn an open letter, Lord Turnbull said
OL,7,Fthe "tragic bombing of Omagh caused
OL,8,Funtold damage to the town and wider
OL,9,Fcommunities".
OL,11,FHe added: "Thirty-one lives were lost,
OL,12,Fhundreds of people were injured and
OL,13,Fthe bombing caused significant damage
OL,14,Fto businesses and property across the
OL,15,Ftown.
OL,17,F"These figures alone, however, do not
OL,18,Ftruly reveal the damage that the
OL,19,Fbombing caused and the real-life human
OL,20,Fimpact."
