OL,6,FLord Turnbull said the purpose of the
OL,7,Fhearings in January and February would
OL,8,Fbe to commemorate those who were
OL,9,Fkilled and also to hear personal
OL,10,Fstatements of people who were affected.
OL,12,FHe said: "This can include people who
OL,13,Fwere injured, both physically and
OL,14,Fpsychologically, those who responded
OL,15,Fin formal roles, local businesses or
OL,16,Fpeople who witnessed the events.
OL,18,F"When I opened the Inquiry earlier
OL,19,Fthis year I said that I wanted to hear
OL,20,Fdirectly from those most affected by
OL,21,Fthe bombing.
OL,26,@tD@JOUzD@AOU
