OL,4,Cbombing to take part in inquiry
OL,6,F"Today I am inviting anyone who wishes
OL,7,Fto share their experiences with the
OL,8,Finquiry to complete a personal
OL,9,Fstatement on how they were affected by
OL,10,Fthe bombing.
OL,12,F"All of your experiences are
OL,13,Fimportant."
OL,15,FLord Turnbull said there is no
OL,16,Fobligation for anyone to participate,
OL,17,Fnor do people need to give oral
OL,18,Fevidence at the hearings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@KO]
