OL,4,Cbombing to take part in inquiry
OL,6,FHe added: "If you wish to share your
OL,7,Fexperience all you need to do is
OL,8,Fcomplete a personal statement form,
OL,9,Fwhich is available on the inquiry
OL,10,Fwebsite.
OL,12,F"There are no rules about how you
OL,13,Fwrite your statement. It should
OL,14,Freflect your own personal experience.
OL,16,F"Not everyone who submits a personal
OL,17,Fstatement will be asked to provide
OL,18,Foral evidence at the commemorative
OL,19,Fhearings in January and February, and
OL,20,Fthere will be no obligation to give
OL,21,Fevidence if you would prefer not to.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
