OL,6,F"But I will read every statement, and
OL,7,Fyour experiences will help to inform
OL,8,Fthe direction and approach of the
OL,9,Finquiry.
OL,11,F"I fully understand what a difficult
OL,12,Ftopic this is and the real risk this
OL,13,Finquiry bears in bringing back the
OL,14,Ftrauma of what happened in Omagh in
OL,15,F1998.
OL,17,F"The Inquiry is also working with Wave
OL,18,FTrauma Centre to provide emotional or
OL,19,Fwellbeing support for those wishing to
OL,20,Fengage with the inquiry."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
