OL,6,FLord Turnbull added: "There have been
OL,7,Fmany investigations into the terrible
OL,8,Fevents of 15 August 1998.
OL,10,F"My inquiry may be the final
OL,11,Fopportunity to get to the truth of
OL,12,Fwhether the bombing could have been
OL,13,Fprevented by the UK state.
OL,15,F"The experiences of those most
OL,16,Faffected on the day will be invaluable
OL,17,Fin helping me do so."
